This module adds utilities common for node (content) types.

= For designers

== Helpers for use in themes

* List nodes: block('node', 'index', :preview | :name, <array of types>)

= For module developers

== URL summary

Create a node:
* /new                   Show descriptions about all node types
Home > Create new content

List previews of nodes, unfiltered: node
* /nodes                 Show previews of all node types
Home > All contents
* /nodes/<page>
* /nodes/<type>          Show previews of a node type
Home > <type>
* /nodes/<type>/<page>

List previews of nodes, filtered by a tag:
* /tags/<tag>/nodes
Home > <tag> > All contents
* /tags/<tag>/nodes/<page>
* /tags/<tag>/nodes/<type>
Home > <tag> > <type>
* /tags/<tag>/nodes/<type>/<page>

== Breadcrumb helpers for use in node controllers

* add_breadcrumbs_new(<type>)
Home > Create new content > Create new <type>
* add_breadcrumbs_show(<type>)
Home >
* add_breadcrumbs_edit(<type>)
Home >
